bzrtp
------------------------------------------
BZRTP is an opensource implementation of ZRTP keys exchange protocol.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libbctoolbox1-5.4.116-1bl1
  libbzrtp-devel-5.4.117-1bl1
  libbzrtp0-5.4.117-1bl1
  libsqlite3_0-3.49.1-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libbctoolbox-devel-5.4.116-1bl1
  libsqlite3-devel-3.49.1-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/BelledonneCommunications/bzrtp

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/BelledonneCommunications/bzrtp/archive/refs/tags/5.4.117.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack bzrtp-5.4.117-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./bzrtp-5.4.117-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/bzrtp-5.4.117-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/bzrtp-5.4.117-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbzrtp0-5.4.117-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbzrtp-devel-5.4.117-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(bzrtp)
  /usr/bin/bzrtp-tester.exe
  /usr/share/bzrtp-tester/patternZIDAlice.sqlite
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/bzrtp.README
  /usr/share/doc/bzrtp/CHANGELOG.md
  /usr/share/doc/bzrtp/LICENSE.txt
  /usr/share/doc/bzrtp/README.md

(libbzrtp0)
  /usr/bin/cygbzrtp-0.dll

(libbzrtp-devel)
  /usr/include/bzrtp/bzrtp.h
  /usr/lib/cmake/bzrtp/BZRTPConfig.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/bzrtp/BZRTPConfigVersion.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/bzrtp/BZRTPTargets-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/bzrtp/BZRTPTargets.cmake
  /usr/lib/libbzrtp.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libbzrtp.pc

